        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/R8LaBCAYicP9nkjO3wlibhBdcRAphCqTAwiaVe837xL1JxqwticBaM1KBjvktia9kw9nYnSL28wjfOfyrQibX373ibcoQ/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg",
          "alt": "Image"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/R8LaBCAYicP9nkjO3wlibhBdcRAphCqTAwOvO0jicZxUkNW59sqAuDw6Wqxb75g542ibtYOkjLicLHtLhyuVeF7K92Q/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg",
          "alt": "Image"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/R8LaBCAYicP9nkjO3wlibhBdcRAphCqTAwKBNibcCTKr8UH1pDibytXvC5xnRkShFBMicV0ztpRYkT25UmgpwLnyibkQ/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg",
          "alt": "Image"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/R8LaBCAYicP9nkjO3wlibhBdcRAphCqTAwLkW8ia1OHjiaUT7A6oLKJole6xBZKXXd2h2bFjKEiaFDpAMzK8ndiaD5rQ/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg",
          "alt": "Image"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "👍到此，魔法已经初步展现Napkin 也支持用户自定义段落组合生成，比如前两段放在一起，出一张图就好了出什么图，出多少图，你说了算~"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/R8LaBCAYicP9nkjO3wlibhBdcRAphCqTAwT7NLzREw70hJqBFyf0LicKHwqRNlGCwkR7Is0LCjdX7zaztMg87wyGg/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg",
          "alt": "Image"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/R8LaBCAYicP9nkjO3wlibhBdcRAphCqTAwbbtib7BAwL51VRJTEwiaWTqTE9Ztv3Pvp5nQ2DWXbjSPxQDLIXkVkEGw/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg",
          "alt": "Image"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "最后一步，希望给标题也生成个图标就好了~Napkin不仅能生成，还可以理解文本内容，推荐更契合的图标你只管写，剩下的ta来"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/R8LaBCAYicP9nkjO3wlibhBdcRAphCqTAwNTXQScahu5bdOjw1JNqA4SH2YnK7Wfa3E9gogZEP36W5zhKSHogbIg/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg",
          "alt": "Image"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/R8LaBCAYicP9nkjO3wlibhBdcRAphCqTAwS1zf0z7aos6KTLVCwnmfJvuZFOxoDxGGHicYicNXPrlxLVS3DVVFudzQ/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg",
          "alt": "Image"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/R8LaBCAYicP9nkjO3wlibhBdcRAphCqTAwWROJ1ibNwY0MdwqAL5ESjiawpd8GCibF8NfmJpp8ll6Ax5zArpf0Y4geQ/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg",
          "alt": "Image"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "📌即使是一段毫无分段的文字，Napkin也可以直接生成图片，根本难不倒ta~最后就是导出PNG/SVG/PDF，包含三种格式"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/R8LaBCAYicP9nkjO3wlibhBdcRAphCqTAw1iaoAIUuON3zibVyuPvE4sQy9ObLQNUKHUEIicAiahdJLZqOicrDAFp2Gaw/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg",
          "alt": "Image"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/R8LaBCAYicP9nkjO3wlibhBdcRAphCqTAwsZqcXe8b6XerrQWFhIdjblB7hm2fNYLLLlFlJsA3ahibns2e6nQ6jZw/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg",
          "alt": "Image"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/R8LaBCAYicP9nkjO3wlibhBdcRAphCqTAwgoHRZ1pM05gpNibicU1mKsM8fViafIktdmrtpLxAE8ibFd51E0GX8wHLww/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg",
          "alt": "Image"
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "text": "三、一些TIPS"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "🚅另一种打开方式，Blank Napkin，就是新建空白页，后续操作完全一致建议使用推荐配色，已经非常完美了所有操作支持 Ctrl+Z，但是不支持 Ctrl+Y，很神奇，只能后退不能前进"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/R8LaBCAYicP9nkjO3wlibhBdcRAphCqTAwJY9z4Qbb8xXBbNHqs9o6icoMaozmhRdvvenTCSo93BXp9fbHwMF4ghg/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg",
          "alt": "Image"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "🎹别无他言，只有赞美，这篇文章并未强调教学使用场景，还是因为ta的使用场景太广泛了！"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "以下是来自一些安利小伙伴的返图"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "教培竞品分析教学设计与技术说明文档"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "感谢KA21的小伙伴们，让我遇到了一个又一个好产品，融入到我的工作生活中~"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "在深度体验之后，也希望能分享给各位，复制→临摹→创新，让我们一起努力~"
        }
