          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Create a charming bakery mascot logo for \"Dough Delight\" featuring an anthropomorphic chef hat or whisk character with rosy cheeks and warm smile, character dusted with flour details, holding or interacting with a signature baked good, warm color palette of golden browns and cream tones, typography that looks slightly puffy like risen dough. Character should evoke homemade w　为\"Dough Delight\"创建一个迷人的烘焙吉祥物标志，以拟人化的厨师帽或打蛋器为角色，带有红润的脸颊和温暖的微笑，角色上撒有面粉细节，手持或与标志性的烘焙食品互动，采用金褐色和奶油色调的温暖配色方案，字体设计略显蓬松，如同发酵的面团。角色应体现家制温暖感和工匠精神，同时具有足够的特色以用于商品和包装设计。armth and craftsmanship while being distinctive enough for merchandise and packaging."
