          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "📝Using a snack spicy strip product image as the base, design 6 flat design backgrounds with different rendered atmospheres reflecting six distinct styles: vibrant dynamic, vintage nostalgic, natural fresh, urban trendy, playful cartoon, and minimalist modern. Each background should highlight a theme, such as \"Spicy Explosion,\" \"Pure Spicy Aroma,\" \"Urban Party,\" \"Fun Spice,\" and \"Ultimate Minimal Spice.\" Accompany the backgrounds with selling point texts like \"Bursting with spicy flavor, unforgettable taste,\" and \"Natural ingredients, healthy and delicious,\" ensuring clear fonts with distinct hierarchy. Focus on color harmony, visual balance, and brand consistency, with high contrast text to ensure accessibility. Each design must feature the brand logo or theme text \"Spicy Strip King.\" aspect ratio 1:1以一个零食辣条产品图片为基础，设计6种不同氛围渲染的扁平化背景，体现六种不同风格：充满活力、自然清新、都市潮流、趣味卡通和极简现代。每个背景都应突出一个主题，如\"辣味爆炸\"、\"纯正辣香\"、\"都市派对\"、\"趣味辣味\"和\"极简辣味\"。配以卖点文案，如\"辣味十足，难忘滋味\"、\"传统工艺，品质保证\"和\"天然配料，健康美味\"，确保字体清晰且层次分明。注重色彩和谐、视觉平衡和品牌一致性，使用高对比度文字以确保可读性。每个设计都必须包含品牌标志或主题文字\"辣条王\"。比例为1:1。"
