          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "💡Image-Generation Prompts (one line per magnet)图像生成提示（每个磁体一行）Use the structure: 使用结构：“ultra-detailed 3D plush dog, light tan fur, mischievous grin, blue bow tie, [scene specifics], premium epoxy fridge magnet mock-up, soft studio light, pastel gradient backdrop, gold foil edge, 32-bit color, photorealistic, isometric view, 1024×1024”“超详细的 3D 毛绒狗、浅棕褐色毛皮、调皮的笑容、蓝色领结、[场景细节]、高级环氧树脂冰箱磁铁模型、柔和的工作室灯光、柔和的渐变背景、金箔边缘、32 位颜色、照片级真实感、等距视图、1024×1024”“…yawning, hugging an oversized white coffee mug with rising steam, Monday morning vibe, espresso brown accent”“… 打哈欠，抱着一个超大的白色咖啡杯，蒸汽不断上升，周一早晨的氛围，浓咖啡棕色的口音”“…wearing sleek office headset, glancing at silver laptop, sarcasm energy, cool gray accent”“… 戴着时尚的办公耳机，瞥了一眼银色的笔记本电脑，讽刺的能量，酷炫的灰色口音”“…sprinting across office floor, flying paper sheets, motion blur, fire-red accent”“… 在办公室地板上冲刺，飞溅的纸张，运动模糊，火红色的点缀”“…furiously typing on mechanical keyboard, blue screen glow, sparks, electric teal accent”“… 在机械键盘上疯狂地打字，蓝屏发光，火花，电蓝绿色口音”“…lounging in mesh office chair, holding sandwich above head, green accent”“… 懒洋洋地躺在网状办公椅上，头顶上放着三明治，绿色点缀”“…raising gold trophy, upward arrow graph behind, confetti sparkle, metallic gold accent”“… 举起金奖杯，后面的向上箭头图，五彩纸屑闪光，金属金点缀”“…front-paw high-five toward camera, sunshine yellow burst”“… 前爪对着镜头击掌，阳光黄爆发”“…wearing thin black glasses, tapping red pen on document stack, speech bubble, crimson accent”“… 戴着薄薄的黑色眼镜，用红笔在文件堆上敲击，对话气泡，深红色口音”“…dancing with colorful confetti swirl, weekend vibe, party purple accent”“… 与五颜六色的五彩纸屑漩涡共舞，周末氛围，派对紫色点缀”“…pointing stick at spotless whiteboard with tick marks, ice blue accent”“… 指向带有刻度线、冰蓝色点缀的一尘不染的白板”“…octopus-style multiple arms: phone, coffee cup, files, calculator, neon lime accent”“… 章鱼式多臂：电话、咖啡杯、文件、计算器、霓虹青柠口音”“…wearing aviator sunglasses, closed laptop, tiny palm tree doodle, coral accent”“… 戴着飞行员太阳镜，戴着封闭的笔记本电脑，戴着小棕榈树涂鸦，戴着珊瑚口音”These prompts ensure consistency while giving the generator clear cues for each unique office scenario.这些提示确保了一致性，同时为每个独特的 Office 场景提供了清晰的提示。I'll continue with the plan to create 12 working professional-themed stickers featuring the dog character. Let's generate the first sticker now.我将继续计划创建 12 个以狗角色为特色的专业主题贴纸。现在让我们生成第一个贴纸。"
